<h2><img src="images/staff/Laurie Birch.jpg" width="129" height="191" style="padding-bottom:10px"/><br />
Laurie Birch, Music Director</h2>
<p>Laurie did her undergraduate work in music at the University of Colorado, Boulder. She later received a Master, Music Education from the University of Bridgeport. She has studied with Dr. Louise Miller, Olga Antonuk, Rosa Rio, and later with Everett Hilty, Don Vollstedt and Cherry Rhodes.</p>
<p>Currently, she is teaching elementary music and chorus in the Milford School system.</p>
<p>She is a member of the American Choral Directors Association, the American Guild of Organists, and the National Association of Music Educators.</p>
<p>She came to First Presbyterian in 2002. </p>
